OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud starts
OL,6,Fto move in from the west overnight
OL,7,Fwhich may produce some spots of rain
OL,8,Fat times. Another mild night to come,
OL,9,Falbeit slightly breezier.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,12,Fweekend but lifting and breaking
OL,13,Fthrough the morning to leave plenty of
OL,14,Fbright and sunny spells. Staying
OL,15,Fbreezy but feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
